  "texts": [
    "Considering important factors mentioned above and key components required when measuring business success, in this paper, we define business success as a capability of a company to become an IPO or be acquired or merged with another company (M &A) and receive more funds from investors or VCs.",
    "On the other hand, failure is defined as a business being formally closed or bankrupted.",
    "With this definition, machine learning tasks are to identify and distinguish companies between failure and success, i.e.",
    "a binary classification or multi-class classification task.",
    "Analyzing features for business prediction is a necessary step in order to build a prediction model."
  ],
